WEBVTT

00:06.441 --> 00:08.225
- And what about this
Marin Calhoun--

00:08.269 --> 00:09.531
where is she now?

00:09.574 --> 00:11.141
- We have reason
to believe her body

00:11.185 --> 00:12.838
was dumped in a lake
near Mosswood.

00:12.882 --> 00:14.144
- Where did you get
that lead?

00:14.188 --> 00:16.016
- From a former
Mosswood member.

00:16.059 --> 00:17.495
- They called it
the purple lake.

00:17.539 --> 00:19.584
I went to the police.
I gave a deposition.

00:19.628 --> 00:22.152
- That's strange--you are
the second person in two days

00:22.196 --> 00:23.849
looking for this tape.

00:23.893 --> 00:25.329
He took it.

00:25.373 --> 00:27.114
- They put Julian
in solitary last night.

00:27.157 --> 00:29.333
I tried to visit him,
but he doesn't want to see me.

00:29.377 --> 00:31.814
He refuses.
- This stuff with Glen Fisher.

00:31.857 --> 00:34.686
- I went to Mosswood
once or twice--that was it.

00:34.730 --> 00:36.036
- Seems like our time for

00:36.079 --> 00:38.038
keeping you up here
with us is over.

00:39.387 --> 00:41.389
- You should name him.

00:41.432 --> 00:43.695
- We'll raise him--
all of us together.

00:43.739 --> 00:47.047
When we offer him up,
release.

00:47.090 --> 00:48.831
- I raised Julian.

00:48.874 --> 00:50.615
I'm his mother,

00:50.659 --> 00:52.356
and something
as trivial as biology

00:52.400 --> 00:54.097
doesn't make that
any less true.

00:54.141 --> 00:56.012
There is something
before we start.

00:56.056 --> 00:57.535
It's about Marin.

00:57.579 --> 00:58.884
She's pregnant.

00:58.928 --> 01:00.103
- We'll raise him.

01:00.147 --> 01:02.366
The child will bind us.

01:02.410 --> 01:04.629
Has she picked a name?

01:12.115 --> 01:19.296
♪

01:31.047 --> 01:38.272
