03:08.840 --> 03:12.583
- So there's this new
dating app thing on your phone.

03:12.627 --> 03:15.369
Helen was telling me
about it.

03:15.412 --> 03:17.327
You should try it out.

03:17.371 --> 03:20.330
It's new on the market,
and, uh...

03:20.374 --> 03:23.681
it's called Rumble?

03:23.725 --> 03:27.032
Uh...or something.

03:27.076 --> 03:29.209
