03:29.252 --> 03:31.863
Although, I guess,
in your case--

03:31.907 --> 03:33.387
Well, how would that work?

03:33.430 --> 03:35.519
- This is not helping.

03:35.563 --> 03:37.521
- All right.
Look, I--

03:37.565 --> 03:39.393
I'm worried about you.

03:39.436 --> 03:41.525
You need
a little pick-me-up,

03:41.569 --> 03:44.876
