03:50.882 --> 03:53.537
You normally stock up.
Laundry's piling up.

03:53.581 --> 03:55.365
- Ow.
Thanks.

03:55.409 --> 03:57.541
- Oh, come on,
I'm trying to make you laugh.

03:57.585 --> 03:59.282
Remember when you used
to do that?

03:59.326 --> 04:02.720
- Sometimes
things aren't funny.

04:02.764 --> 04:04.722
I got to get
back to the station.

04:04.766 --> 04:07.725
- Don't go mad.

04:07.769 --> 04:09.814
- I'm fine.

04:14.776 --> 04:16.256
- Hi, sweetie.

04:16.299 --> 04:18.388
Thank you
for letting me visit you.

04:18.432 --> 04:21.043
I hated not being able
to see you.

04:25.787 --> 04:28.268
Did you get hurt?

04:28.311 --> 04:30.270
Who hurt you?

04:34.796 --> 04:36.537
I don't know.

04:39.453 --> 04:41.542
- Julian,
who did this to you?

04:47.939 --> 04:51.291
- Did they make you
take something?

04:51.334 --> 04:54.424
What did they give you?

04:54.468 --> 04:55.904
What did you people
do to my son?

04:55.947 --> 04:57.775
He can barely speak.
- Ma'am, please sit down.

04:57.819 --> 04:59.777
- Don't call me "ma'am."
He's been medicated.

04:59.821 --> 05:01.344
You can't do that
without my permission.

05:01.388 --> 05:02.998
- If he's a harm
to himself or others,

05:03.041 --> 05:05.435
the doctors can give him
something to make him a little--

05:05.479 --> 05:06.784
What doctor?

05:06.828 --> 05:07.959
I want to speak to
this doctor right now.

05:08.003 --> 05:08.960
- Ma'am, please sit down.

05:09.004 --> 05:10.005
- I will not sit down.

05:10.048 --> 05:12.094
And do not call me "ma'am."

05:12.137 --> 05:14.792
♪

05:16.838 --> 05:23.888
♪

05:39.861 --> 05:43.647
- Excuse me. Can I, uh,
talk to you for a minute?

05:43.691 --> 05:48.478
That guy you were just with,
you know him very well?

05:51.046 --> 05:54.354
- I'm curious...

05:54.397 --> 05:57.357
'cause I saw you here
with him two days ago

05:57.400 --> 05:59.184
and the night before that.

05:59.228 --> 06:00.664
- Okay.

06:00.708 --> 06:02.492
So?

06:02.536 --> 06:05.495
- I hear he can get
a little rough.

06:05.539 --> 06:07.062
You know anything about that?

06:07.105 --> 06:09.499
- I don't talk to cops.
- Maybe you should.

06:09.543 --> 06:12.720
