right now--you know that.

06:12.763 --> 06:15.853
Glen Fisher doesn't
even like to have sex.

06:17.420 --> 06:19.030
You got nothing.

06:21.903 --> 06:24.035
- Hey.

06:24.079 --> 06:27.212
Your foot there.

06:27.256 --> 06:29.345
