06:37.527 --> 06:40.008
- I'm not at liberty to say.

06:40.051 --> 06:43.054
That's the order, coming off
an incident yesterday.

06:43.098 --> 06:44.708
What happened?

06:44.752 --> 06:46.536
- I'm sorry, but
that's, uh, confidential.

06:46.580 --> 06:48.495
Excuse me for one second.

06:48.538 --> 06:51.454
- Yeah...

06:59.114 --> 07:02.160
- I know you.

07:05.947 --> 07:09.254
- You're the gent who visited
that floozy.

07:09.298 --> 07:12.736
She got tranq'd.

07:12.780 --> 07:15.739
- Yeah, sorry to hear
about that.

07:15.783 --> 07:17.741
Any idea what provoked it?

07:17.785 --> 07:20.918
- Eh, she got a call
at the start of afternoon rec,

07:20.962 --> 07:23.268
