you lose TV rights, no gum.

07:27.621 --> 07:30.537
- She stayed on the phone,
and they gave her meds?

07:30.580 --> 07:33.453
- Nah, she got off
and went ballistic.

07:33.496 --> 07:36.281
- Anybody hear who it was
that called her?

07:36.325 --> 07:38.283
- Detective.
- Yeah, just--

07:38.327 --> 07:40.590
- Please.

07:40.634 --> 07:43.680
- She said it was Satan.

07:49.991 --> 07:52.080
- Keller PD,
Officer Brickowski.

07:52.123 --> 07:54.474
- Yeah, hey, Brick.
It's me again.

07:54.517 --> 07:56.606
