calling me here.

08:09.750 --> 08:12.317
You're gonna get me in trouble.- No, no, I know, I know.

08:12.361 --> 08:13.971
You did nothing.

08:14.015 --> 08:15.320
Right.

08:15.364 --> 08:22.545
♪

08:39.823 --> 08:47.091
