13:58.011 --> 14:01.449
- I know you did things
you're ashamed of.

14:01.492 --> 14:05.366
♪

14:05.409 --> 14:08.369
- Fine.

14:08.412 --> 14:09.979
Fine.

14:14.070 --> 14:15.376
Sit down.

14:15.419 --> 14:18.553
♪

14:18.596 --> 14:21.904
I'll tell you everything.

14:42.620 --> 14:44.753
- Ugh.

14:46.798 --> 14:49.149
- Uh, yeah, I'm fine.

14:52.979 --> 14:54.937
- It's nothing.

14:54.981 --> 14:58.419
- Bess.

14:58.462 --> 15:00.508
Let me see.

15:05.469 --> 15:07.602
Oh, my God.
What happened?

15:07.645 --> 15:09.430
- It was just the session
last night.

15:09.473 --> 15:12.955
I was partnered with Vic,
and he had a breakthrough.

15:12.999 --> 15:14.957
- It was...good.

15:15.001 --> 15:16.437
He tapped
into some family stuff.

15:16.480 --> 15:18.221
- No, no.

15:18.265 --> 15:21.746
I was standing
in the wrong place by the rock.

15:21.790 --> 15:25.968
And he was so deep in it,
I didn't want to...

15:26.012 --> 15:28.057
stop him.

15:30.494 --> 15:32.670
I get it now.

15:32.714 --> 15:35.108
It's part of my work, too.

15:35.151 --> 15:37.458
