would welcome you back?

17:14.946 --> 17:16.905
- This is different.

17:16.948 --> 17:18.689
- No.

17:18.733 --> 17:20.561
No, Vera, it's not.

17:20.604 --> 17:23.912
It's the same small-minded,

17:23.955 --> 17:26.741
middle-class fear.

17:26.784 --> 17:32.268
♪

