18:29.108 --> 18:30.979
- Good job.
- Here you go.

18:31.022 --> 18:32.589
- Good job.
- Oh.

18:32.633 --> 18:34.025
Oh.
Yeah.

18:34.069 --> 18:35.505
- There you go.
- Hold on to him.

